代表無愛情<br />\n就算有感覺而開始都始終有一日會無"},{"pid":"e5469b000c74b289b2fc47aa6e6d43c854c999e4","tid":202854,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:04:29.000Z","msg":"同ex散左3年<br />\n最近遇到個鐘意既人<br />\n本來無欲無求過一世咪好<br />\n點解要俾個人我囉囉攣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果種不斷等佢覆msg 已讀不回會驚一餐既感覺其實好難受<br />\n佢唔止對你一個好 佢對個個都咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e725b4372dffadba4c2ab15fe388a5f6e4df20","tid":202854,"uid":90706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T22:45:14.000Z","msg":"雖然話 習慣佐就冇乜所謂 <br />\n但我覺得感情，或者勇敢愛 喜歡，呢d嘢 真係唔可以話冇佐之後習慣一下就冇嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n尤其我地日日都接收唔同信息，好嘅壞嘅～ <br />\n但大家有冇感覺到，當呢種習慣真係變成一種習慣， 感情於妳於我就會開始覺得並非冇必要，但心底裡總會話習慣佐就ok嘎喇 ，緣未到嘖 <br />\n 其實呢種習慣好可怕，妳/你大概好想去拍拖，好想喜歡一個人，但又唔想為拍拖而拍拖；你可能唔想去拍拖，但到佐某d之後卻不自覺地想，倘若我身邊也有那麽一個他/她 似乎也是不錯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但當那一刻過後，熱情，衝動退卻後，那個該死的「習慣」又會走出黎同你講「習慣就冇嘢嘎喇」 <br />\n如是者，不斷循環 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n細思極恐 <br />\n當到了某一刻發現，咦 這個她/他不錯呢！ 然後你/妳也只是在心底裡想想，嗯 確實不錯，然後抬起腳繼續向前行，大不了回頭望一眼，到最後 你依然都只會是一個人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nps 並非不想愛，而是漸漸有那麽些許的麻木該如何愛 互勉，年多前帽事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 的我"},{"pid":"6cced035d8bb912af6f4ee24fcdfe0c298034853","tid":202854,"uid":16483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T23:06:16.000Z","msg":"單身左三年幾 慢慢你會習慣 覺得講咩都曬氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7162bf73ffb628cd3d5ab3ab1ce91008793c6414","tid":202854,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:55:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實種感覺無左就無左<br />\n但無左又唔代表無愛情<br />\n就算有感覺而開始都始終有一日會無</blockquote><br />\n現時大了 那種心跳難重演"},{"pid":"ad35203b7d525ceddea1d76e7c96613bd4769976","tid":202854,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T02:57:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同ex散左3年<br />\n最近遇到個鐘意既人<br />\n本來無欲無求過一世咪好<br />\n點解要俾個人我囉囉攣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n果種不斷等佢覆msg 已讀不回會驚一餐既感覺其實好難受<br />\n佢唔止對你一個好 佢對個個都咁好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有對象可能係好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過人大咗驚受傷總會保留自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望你果個人係岩你 幸幸福福啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce2e8e6dd04f16ba2fe163211caa70d57e70c8f","tid":202854,"uid":3980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前中學 兩個人果種單純又純粹既感覺<br />\n冇目的 冇機心 純粹係自然走近對方<br />\n慢慢就會一齊 愈黎愈鍾意對方<br />\n就算到最後 彼此感覺淡咗 都係一段份外美好既回憶<br />\n<br />\n但人大咗 我漸漸搵唔番果種簡單 心跳既感覺<br />\n速食文化既流行 每個人靠近都係建基於外表<br />\n人與人之間既關係變得好淺薄<br />\n我再搵唔到理由去愛上任何人<br />\n都投放唔到自己真摯既感情<br />\n<br />\n係俗世既洪流之中 此刻我感到空虛</blockquote><br />\n單身左好耐？</blockquote><br />\n一年多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一年多啲咁快可以睇化<br />\n<br />\n你叫啲出世單身到宜家既人情何以堪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 單身左八年"},{"pid":"8f03c6de476a38c5b90d5cab662dac1969c57067","tid":202854,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然話 習慣佐就冇乜所謂 <br />\n但我覺得感情，或者勇敢愛 喜歡，呢d嘢 真係唔可以話冇佐之後習慣一下就冇嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n尤其我地日日都接收唔同信息，好嘅壞嘅～ <br />\n但大家有冇感覺到，當呢種習慣真係變成一種習慣， 感情於妳於我就會開始覺得並非冇必要，但心底裡總會話習慣佐就ok嘎喇 ，緣未到嘖 <br />\n 其實呢種習慣好可怕，妳/你大概好想去拍拖，好想喜歡一個人，但又唔想為拍拖而拍拖；你可能唔想去拍拖，但到佐某d之後卻不自覺地想，倘若我身邊也有那麽一個他/她 似乎也是不錯呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n但當那一刻過後，熱情，衝動退卻後，那個該死的「習慣」又會走出黎同你講「習慣就冇嘢嘎喇」 <br />\n如是者，不斷循環 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n細思極恐 <br />\n當到了某一刻發現，咦 這個她/他不錯呢！ 然後你/妳也只是在心底裡想想，嗯 確實不錯，然後抬起腳繼續向前行，大不了回頭望一眼，到最後 你依然都只會是一個人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nps 並非不想愛，而是漸漸有那麽些許的麻木該如何愛 互勉，年多前帽事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 的我</blockquote><br />\n好長既文 好深既感慨<br />\n其實習慣係現實要我地做既野<br />\n每個人都係架啦 總會有少少想擺脫現實果種無奈<br />\n但最後都係不得不屈服 因為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你明架啦<br />\n加油啊巴打 希望你既緣份儘快來臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ebdd0b79efc7510b50fcf603ca94f7232b5586b","tid":202854,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前中學 兩個人果種單純又純粹既感覺<br />\n冇目的 冇機心 純粹係自然走近對方<br />\n慢慢就會一齊 愈黎愈鍾意對方<br />\n就算到最後 彼此感覺淡咗 都係一段份外美好既回憶<br />\n<br />\n但人大咗 我漸漸搵唔番果種簡單 心跳既感覺<br />\n速食文化既流行 每個人靠近都係建基於外表<br />\n人與人之間既關係變得好淺薄<br />\n我再搵唔到理由去愛上任何人<br />\n都投放唔到自己真摯既感情<br />\n<br />\n係俗世既洪流之中 此刻我感到空虛</blockquote><br />\n單身左好耐？</blockquote><br />\n一年多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一年多啲咁快可以睇化<br />\n<br />\n你叫啲出世單身到宜家既人情何以堪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 單身左八年</blockquote><br />\nOk 你食鹽多過我食米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ca2aca05873e8e8c37c713bc8afd72fc9160187","tid":202854,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:06:09.000Z","msg":"巴定絲，做乜唔試下搵另一半？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9373c18a368609c7a2951c64d6248b8abf0315a","tid":202854,"uid":50347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:07:22.000Z","msg":"gay既係難搵啲"},{"pid":"b8bc539940b37b989a5103d55b9ea630432ab6d5","tid":202854,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:21:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴定絲，做乜唔試下搵另一半？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇對象/對象唔適合掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8082f4d8a4b68a924caa1a00b9f8cd0e38b89470","tid":202854,"uid":21483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴定絲，做乜唔試下搵另一半？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我唔識答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇對象/對象唔適合掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n工作環境無適合既對象？或者平時周圍？"},{"pid":"4075fbf8d5b2d51dda3e25b616d4f89c630a14f2","tid":202854,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T03:38:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>gay既係難搵啲</blockquote>"},{"pid":"2db322e6e42bd7137099d249a716b970f3df73ef","tid":202854,"uid":65256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T04:49:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>巴定絲，做乜唔試下搵另一半？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><b